description: Our unigue little food truck has a small easy to choose from menu with cajun-style food such as red beans and rice, Jambalaya, shrimp creole poboys and more... Food is mmmm mmmm Good. We also serve concession stand style items such as hot dogs, nachos and salad..We have the best service and really know how to get the food out in friendly, fast and accurate way..Please do not hesitate to book us on your next event..Thank you!
name: Cajun on the Go! Food Truck
